(- Start scan \(ZIP\): `POST /api/scan/zip`) Tj
T*
(- Start scan \(Paste\): `POST /api/scan/paste`) Tj
T*
(- Scan status: `GET /api/scan/{scan_id}`) Tj
T*
(- Live logs \(SSE\): `GET /api/scan/{scan_id}/stream`) Tj
T*
(- Reports: `GET /api/report/{scan_id}?format=pdf|json`) Tj
T*
(- System config: `GET /api/config`) Tj
T*
T*
(---) Tj
T*
T*
(NOTES ON MODEL ROUTING) Tj
T*
T*
(Model selection is automatic by policy:) Tj
T*
(- `ROUTING_MODE=auto` uses `AUTO_ROUTER_MODEL` \(OpenRouter auto\)) Tj
T*
(- `ROUTING_MODE=fixed` uses `MODEL_NAME`) Tj
T*
(- `ROUTING_MODE=learning` uses the learning store if available, otherwise auto) Tj
T*
T*
(The UI no longer asks for a model because the system already chooses the best one.) Tj
T*
ET
